---
title: Smokey Venison Steak & Creamy Potatoes with Cherry Sauce & Lemony Greens
description: Tender seared venison steak is the star of this show, flavoured with our Kiwi spice blend! Get ready for a smokey, savoury taste sensation, made all the better in this meal drenched in a sweet and tangy cherry sauce.

